748
01:16:26,649 --> 01:16:30,345
Yuri itu orang yang lucu./
Ia berlatih yoga.

749
01:16:31,720 --> 01:16:35,354
'Ceruk.'/ Ia cerita
padamu soal ceruk?

750
01:16:36,692 --> 01:16:39,559
"Ceruk di Koningin Astrid Park."

751
01:16:47,970 --> 01:16:51,451
Aku tahu kau
harus melakukan ini.

752
01:16:51,551 --> 01:16:53,390
Terlalu ramai di sini.

753
